sequenceDiagram
    participant pytest as "pytest Runner"
    participant fixture as "freeze_time Fixture"
    participant test as "Test Function"
    participant fake as "FakeGraph/FakeVectorStore"
    participant code as "MemoryConsolidator"
    
    Note over pytest,code: SETUP PHASE
    
    pytest->>fixture: Execute autouse fixture
    fixture->>fixture: Patch datetime.now()
    
    pytest->>test: Call test function
    test->>fake: Configure mock data
    Note over fake: Set relationship_counts,<br/>sample_rows, etc.
    
    Note over pytest,code: EXECUTION PHASE
    
    test->>code: Create MemoryConsolidator(fake)
    test->>code: Call method under test<br/>(e.g., calculate_relevance_score)
    
    code->>fake: graph.query(cypher, params)
    fake->>fake: Match query pattern
    fake->>fake: Return configured data
    fake-->>code: FakeResult
    
    code-->>test: Return result
    
    Note over pytest,code: VERIFICATION PHASE
    
    test->>test: Assert result values
    test->>fake: Verify state changes<br/>(deleted, archived, queries)
    
    test-->>pytest: Pass/Fail
    
    Note over pytest,code: CLEANUP PHASE
    
    fixture->>fixture: Restore original datetime
    pytest->>pytest: Report results